teal.sim.function

Class VectorGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • teal.core.AbstractElement
      • teal.sim.function.VectorGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.beans.PropertyChangeListener, java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener, HasID, TElement, THasPropertyChange, Stepping, TSimElement

    public class VectorGenerator
extends AbstractElement
implements TSimElement, Stepping
    A simple vector generator, this outputs a sequence of Vector3ds, defined by mode. It is over-kill for this to implement Integratable, but we need to think about that whole interface.
